name: complex_if_add_common_right_factor
section: control-if-arithmetic
args: cond:Bool common:Int a:Int b:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: A common right addend can be lifted across an if expression.
law: (= (fuzz-add (if {cond} {a} {b}) {common}) (if {cond} (fuzz-add {a} {common}) (fuzz-add {b} {common})))
